<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="hero-card rise-enter">
    <view class="hero-eyebrow">
      <text>FEEDBACK</text>
      <text>{{completedRatings}} / {{totalDishes}} 已完成</text>
    </view>
    <view class="hero-title">把这顿饭的反馈留下来，下次菜单会更懂你。</view>
    <view class="hero-subtitle">一张卡只评价一道菜，先打分，再补一句感受，整页会清楚很多。</view>
    <view class="progress-card">
      <view class="progress-copy">
        <text class="progress-label">评价进度</text>
        <text class="progress-value">{{ratingProgress}}%</text>
      </view>
      <view class="progress-track">
        <view class="progress-fill" style="width: {{ratingProgress}}%;"></view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card section-shell rating-summary fade-enter" wx:if="{{selectedDishes.length > 0}}">
    <view class="section-head compact-head">
      <view class="section-title-wrap">
        <text class="section-kicker">QUICK GUIDE</text>
        <text class="section-title">怎么填更省事</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="summary-grid">
      <view class="summary-item">
        <text class="summary-value">1</text>
        <text class="summary-label">先点星级</text>
      </view>
      <view class="summary-item">
        <text class="summary-value">2</text>
        <text class="summary-label">再补一句感受</text>
      </view>
      <view class="summary-item">
        <text class="summary-value">{{completedRatings}}</text>
        <text class="summary-label">已完成反馈</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="rating-list section-shell" wx:if="{{selectedDishes.length > 0}}">
    <view class="surface-card rating-card fade-enter" wx:for="{{selectedDishes}}" wx:key="id">
      <view class="rating-header-row">
        <image class="rating-image" src="{{item.displayImage || item.image}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
        <view class="rating-copy">
          <view class="chip-row">
            <text class="chip chip-light">{{item.category}}</text>
            <text class="chip chip-mint">{{item.difficulty || '简单'}}</text>
          </view>
          <text class="rating-name">{{item.name}}</text>
          <text class="rating-desc">{{item.cookingTime || '30分钟'}} · {{item.calories || '--'}} kcal</text>
        </view>
        <view class="status-chip {{item.rating > 0 || item.comment ? 'done' : ''}}">
          <text>{{item.rating > 0 || item.comment ? '已填写' : '待填写'}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="editor-block">
        <text class="editor-title">这道菜整体怎么样？</text>
        <text class="editor-helper strong-helper">1 分一般，5 分是下次还想再吃。</text>
        <view class="star-row">
          <view class="star {{index < item.rating ? 'active' : ''}}" wx:for="{{[1,2,3,4,5]}}" wx:key="*this" bindtap="setRating" data-dish-id="{{item.id}}" data-rating="{{index + 1}}">
            <text>★</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <text class="editor-helper">{{item.rating > 0 ? '已打 ' + item.rating + ' 分' : '点一下星星就能完成打分'}}</text>
      </view>

      <view class="editor-block">
        <view class="comment-head">
          <text class="editor-title">补一句具体感受</text>
          <text class="comment-count">{{item.comment ? item.comment.length : 0}} / 200</text>
        </view>
        <textarea class="comment-box" placeholder="比如：味道很稳、下次想少一点辣、份量刚刚好。" value="{{item.comment}}" bindinput="onCommentInput" data-dish-id="{{item.id}}" maxlength="200"></textarea>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card section-shell empty-panel fade-enter" wx:else>
    <text class="empty-title">还没有需要评价的菜单</text>
    <text class="empty-desc">回到首页先选几道菜，评价页就会自动出现对应内容。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="bottom-dock rise-enter" wx:if="{{!sharePanelVisible}}">
    <view class="dock-content rating-dock-panel">
      <view class="dock-copy rating-dock-copy">
        <text class="dock-title">已完成 {{completedRatings}} / {{totalDishes}} 道反馈</text>
        <text class="dock-desc">至少评价一道菜就可以提交，也可以直接跳过本轮反馈。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="rating-dock-actions">
        <button class="ghost-btn rating-skip" bindtap="skipRating">先跳过</button>
        <button class="primary-btn rating-submit" bindtap="submitRating" disabled="{{!canSubmit}}">提交评价</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="share-panel-mask" wx:if="{{sharePanelVisible}}" bindtap="closeSharePanel"></view>
  <view class="share-panel rise-enter" wx:if="{{sharePanelVisible}}">
    <view class="share-panel-head">
      <text class="share-panel-title">分享给朋友</text>
      <text class="share-panel-desc">这里会直接拉起微信原生分享面板，不再只是复制到剪贴板。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="share-panel-body">
      <text class="share-panel-label">本次反馈</text>
      <text class="share-panel-summary">{{shareSummary}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="share-panel-actions">
      <button class="ghost-btn share-secondary" bindtap="closeSharePanel">先不分享</button>
      <button class="primary-btn share-primary" open-type="share">立即分享</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
